# Code owners for this repo.
#
# GitHub reads this file to decide whose review is required on a PR.
# The `main_protect` ruleset has `require_code_owner_review: true`, so
# without this file that rule is a no-op. With it, the owners listed
# below are auto-requested as reviewers on any PR that touches matching
# paths.
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Patterns work like .gitignore, but order matters — the LAST matching
# rule wins. Put broad rules first, narrow rules last.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
